<title type="html"><![CDATA[5/12(Thu) Major drought drives 20M toward hunger in Africa/Robot living in Antarctic penguin colony (Host: George)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=616&amp;p=639#p639"><![CDATA[
Major drought drives 20M toward hunger in Africa/Robot living in Antarctic penguin colony (Host: George)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Session I<br />Major drought drives 20M toward hunger in Africa<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://taipeitimes.com/News/world/archives/2022/05/05/2003777758">https://taipeitimes.com/News/world/arch ... 2003777758</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Question:<br />1. How does the drought affect Africans, especially children under the age of six?<br />2. What is the number of hungry people due to drought through 2022?<br />3.“Dire conditions in the Horn of Africa have been amplified by Russia’s war in Ukraine, which has contributed to soaring food and fuel costs……” Do you agree or disagree? What are the reasons?<br />4. Do you agree that extreme weather events are happening with increased frequency and intensity due to climate change? Why? <br />5. Taiwan recently got the worst drought in 56 years in June 2021. Do you think that it will happen again this year? Why or why not? Is our government well prepared to face the extreme climate?<br /><br />Session II<br />A robot lives in this Antarctic penguin colony. It's trying to save them<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://edition.cnn.com/2022/04/29/world/robots-antarctica-penguins-climate-scn/index.html">https://edition.cnn.com/2022/04/29/worl ... index.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. What features does ECHO have? What does ECHO look like? <br />2. How does ECHO help the scientists to monitor Antarctic penguins?<br />3. How do the scientists tag Antarctic penguins? What are the reasons that scientists need to tag them?<br />4. Why does the number of Antarctic penguins decline rapidly?<br />5. What kind of indications do Antarctic penguins indicate in the food chains and the environment? <br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Sat May 07, 2022 9:10 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
